      "column": "left",
      "text": "Buhfu taim KUNGA W\nlabs Prahts pee tubkftofcheem\nAuneem? jeb pee Defmits tubk-\nstochahm Etjes-Uppehni? Arrig\neß fawu Pirmdfuntu dolſchu\npreekſch mannas Bahrfahpfcha-\nnas/ mannas Mecfas Augli\npreekſch mannas Dwehfeles\nGrehkeim?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch irr tew ſtabſtiß/\nak Zilweks! kas labs irraid/ un\nko praffa tas KUNGS no te-\nwim/ neka darriht/ kas teeja irr/\nSchehlastibu uuhleht/ un pa-\nfeüigi ſtaigaht ar tawa Deewa\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Balknis\nfanks pahr to Pilſfahtn/(tawn\nWahrdn redſehs paſcha Buh-\nfchana/) Klanfajs Zilts/ kas to\nirr fa-aizinajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tatſchu wehl ta Besdee-\nwiga Namina paleek besdeewi-\ngas Mantas/ un ta natdiga ma-\nsa Eepa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Arrig es ſchkihts buhtu\nar besdeevisa Swarra/ un ar\nweena Maifa no wiltigeem\nSwarra-Akimixeem?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zaur ko winnas Bagga-\nti ar Warras-Darba peepildahs/\nun winnas Eedſhwotaji Mellus\nrunna/ un winnu Mehle irr wil-\ntiga winnu Mutte.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ir es eefahſchu\ntewi wahju darriht/ un ſittifchu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu ehdiſt/ bet ne pee-eh-\ndiſt/ un tu tapſt tawa Widdii\nuospaidthts/ un ko tu guhſti/ to\ntu tomehr ne aisneffſt/ un ko tu\naisneffſt/ to nodobſchu es Sol-\nvikam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu fehſt/ bet ne pkansſ/\ntu mihtt Etjes Ohgas/ bet ar\nEtjes ne fwaidifeeß/ un januu\nWihnu/ bet Wihnu ne dserſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tur tohp tas Ccerad-\ndums Amrus zeenihts/ un tas\nDarbe ta Akaba Namma/ un\njuhs ſtaigajat winao Padohinde.\nTadeht nodobſchu es tevi par\nPohſtiſchann/ un winnas Ge-\ndſhwotajns/ ka tee taps iſtwil-\npeti/ ta neffifeet juhs to Neewa-\nſchannu manno Lauschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "un pohtiſchu tevitawo Grehen\ndeht.\n"
    }
